text: We met with friends at this spot for lunch. we heard about this spot from a lot of people.  Well, it was very nice. the crew were so friendly and we felt excellent. The meal was fresh and delicious. We loved this spot a lot and we will visit this place again. Highly recommended.

The service was good and very efficient getting the pizza to me in about 5 minutes at lunch time. Highly recommend checking this place out if you haven't; this was my first time.
